      },
      "description": "Sub-agent cost from dispatch.agent span-end events (context_session_id join key — both series now group by context_session_id for an apples-to-apples comparison). Total cost from run.complete. The gap is root-agent-only cost.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "maxDataPoints": 2000,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
